{"tid":1306027,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論] 香港會否有革命？關鍵係...","createTime":"2019-07-11T04:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T05:56:09.000Z","uid":26332,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d9cc31b2d798ce9a9f4411521356eb6e009bb97f","tid":1306027,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:13:15.000Z","msg":"革命需要導火線，只係需要一單好震撼嘅事件就可以kick start，好似一戰正式開始，係因為奧匈帝國暗殺事件<br />\n<br />\n講白啲，除咗死人冧樓，諗唔到其他原因有革命出現....<br />\n<br />\n如果有人犧牲，例如後生仔，甚至未成年，俾黑警打死/開槍殺死等，又或者關乎貼身利益，例如樓爆樓價跌到低過sars，先會夠震撼性去kick start一場革命<br />\n<br />\n長期抗爭唔會有革命出現，一來會消耗民意憤怒等，二來會令更多人無心戀戰而放棄，除非不斷有激嬲市民嘅事，不斷fuel民眾情緒<br />\n<br />\n只要民眾憤怒去到一個臨界點，就有條件激發革命<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>就好似有一缸油，你不斷消耗，自然最後會無晒<br />\n不斷入油，亦唔代表會着火，着火只需要一支火柴就搞掂</ins></strong>"},{"pid":"0977efb2ec59e182e8753820bd1cca4438af5f87","tid":1306027,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c9bf006eb82e8fbebf921aea6542ff93b6cccb6","tid":1306027,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"321d3ce4b7f85f7d2f350358ec627eca8f13ed9d","tid":1306027,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:16:44.000Z","msg":"連拳頭交都大條道理唔敢打<br />\n點會革命"},{"pid":"e0fe7f3fb1675fd6470a805e36461384d52f5142","tid":1306027,"uid":268855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ec3761de700be1390d5a6b5ba974dfb1bd7e60","tid":1306027,"uid":263464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:19:24.000Z","msg":"7.11 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8527%2F5csivkdzoxKq11rtK